Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.39,0:01:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三話\N悲傷的劍士\N斬斷過去的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.37,0:01:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷道場踏出再建的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.61,0:01:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寄食的劍客 劍心加入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.38,0:01:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一個弟子是明神禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.65,0:01:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼訓練的第三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.85,0:02:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也先從深呼吸開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.79,0:02:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼睛閉起來。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.46,0:02:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷活心流的第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.87,0:02:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼活心流嘛我已經厭煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.61,0:02:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候\N你才會教我對抗敵人的方法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這想法就不對了！\N我不是說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.78,0:02:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活心流是保護人的劍法了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.81,0:02:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護人？哇啊。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.65,0:02:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！我是為了要\N成為強者才到這裏來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要保護人的劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.99,0:02:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而希望你教我打倒敵人的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.69,0:02:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生的劍法沒有打算留在後世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.70,0:02:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥的師父是小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等！等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你飯團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.61,0:02:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飯團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的！劍心這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫人家要成為強者的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這麼壞的小孩子推給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你吃自己做的不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.57,0:03:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是劍心做的比較好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.30,0:03:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的你的好勝心\N雖然可怕的有點像我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是感覺像是\N擁有成績不好的弟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.35,0:03:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我也是覺得你很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是看到那劍心之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是。。真不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼厲害的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼待在這\N名不經傳的小道館呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂阿熏劍心到道是何人物呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是。。什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那對敵的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像殺了很多人的感覺。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了！！\N那傢伙真正的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.95,0:04:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會是以前的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山賊吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在一定被警察追捕著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太帥了！！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.14,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實是。。。\N為什麼會成為流浪人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是完成明治維新的志士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府末年的動亂之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心為什麼會消失呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是個謎。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.92,0:04:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謠傳說殺了不該殺的人。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道太多的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.90,0:05:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被明治政府追殺著。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是。。！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是小熏小姐的午餐！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快還給我！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個笨蛋！！\N為什麼要有秘密呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.90,0:05:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害人家這麼擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把真的事情說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.87,0:05:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行。。\N不可以問別人的過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.25,0:05:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那。。那個\N問你這種事也許不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是一點點就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.22,0:06:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？什麼事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.36,0:06:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去買豆腐了今天要吃好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.17,0:06:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連我的份也要幫我煮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是。是嗎。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.44,0:06:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼你們這些傢伙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這道場的負責人叫來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.11,0:06:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要麻煩人之前\N首先要自報姓名吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.81,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你。你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我，我是神谷熏師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎不是很無禮嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.16,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看那樣子連三歲小孩也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,署長！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.33,0:06:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心。。\N拔刀齊應該是在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.47,0:06:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊？是指殺人拔刀齊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是劍心嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.41,0:06:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假拔刀齊被捕的人證實了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是在這道場裏。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果隱藏了國家罪犯是犯罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.52,0:07:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心你說劍心做了什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.25,0:07:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是等在外面的人\N才知道政府機密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我來搜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.66,0:07:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.16,0:07:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟拔刀齊一起你想死刑嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去通知劍心\N回來會被捕的！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.74,0:07:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿。。阿熏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.94,0:07:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.41,0:07:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要了。。總算讓我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.39,0:07:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要。。見面了\N緋村。。拔刀齊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小雀也。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.87,0:07:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要太急否則豆腐會破掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看有帶刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙真是大膽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.21,0:08:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大白天的就違抗廢刀令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.35,0:08:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者你想在\N劍客警官的面前一決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.52,0:08:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝了我就讓你逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有小孩子在。。。\N求求你不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這是逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.79,0:08:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逆刃刀？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈。。那東西\N連一隻老鼠都不能殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,窩囊廢！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.47,0:08:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經沒關繫了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.15,0:08:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是壞人，把我們豆腐弄倒了\N不道歉是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.15,0:08:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開！鬼叫的小孩給我讓開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.09,0:08:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍客警官大人要通過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍客警官隊。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.33,0:08:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小偷你死了這條心吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.61,0:09:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饒了我吧\N這是我偶發起的歹意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你們饒了他吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.95,0:09:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只被拿走一條擦手巾而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.32,0:09:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用麻煩各位劍客警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏有我們在就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些鄉下的三等巡查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.36,0:09:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要對我們抗議嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道我們是薩摩的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不我。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.74,0:09:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.54,0:09:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說些什麼。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.04,0:09:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是劍客警官隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被挑選出來的精選部隊。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你們這些無名小卒不一樣\N被允許帶刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之殺人是被政府所准許的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，拔刀吧。。\N會把你殺了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.79,0:09:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心劍心！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心你在哪裏呢？！
